Title: Regional expression profiles of autistic brain
Description: The regional autism dataset from Voineagu et al. 2011, extracted from the Gene Expression Omnibus (accession number GSE28521).

Title: Metadata for regional expression profiles of autistic brain
Description: The metadata for the regional autism dataset (Voineagu et al. 2011).

Title: Autisic brain SummarizedExperiment
Description: SummarizedExperiment object for the regional autism dataset (Voineagu et al. 2011).

Title: Regional astrocyte expression profiles in experimental autoimmune encephalomyelitis
Description: The astrocyte dataset from Itoh et al. PNAS. 2018, extracted from the supplementary materials.

Title: Metadata for regional astrocyte expression profiles in experimental autoimmune encephalomyelitis
Description: The metadata for the astrocyte Ribotag dataset (Itoh et al. PNAS. 2018).

Title: Astrocyte weighted gene coexpression networks
Description: The astrocyte networks from Tommasini and Fogel, BMC Bioinformatics, 2023. derived from the astrocyte Ribotag data from Itoh et al. PNAS. 2018.

Title: Astrocyte Ribotag SummarizedExperiment
Description: SummarizedExperiment object for the astrocyte Ribotag dataset (Itoh et al. PNAS. 2018).

Title: Timecourse expression profiles of tau pathology in entorhinal cortex
Description: The tau dataset from Castanho et al. Cell Rep. 2020, extracted from GEO (GSE125957) processed data file.

Title: Metadata for timecourse expression profiles of tau pathology in entorhinal cortex
Description: The metadata for the tau timecourse dataset (Castanho et al. Cell Rep. 2020).

Title: Tau weighted gene coexpression networks
Description: The tau networks from Tommasini and Fogel, BMC Bioinformatics, 2023. derived from the tau timecourse data from Castanho et al. Cell Rep. 2020.

Title: Tau pathology SummarizedExperiment
Description: SummarizedExperiment object for the tau timecourse dataset (Castanho et al. Cell Rep. 2020).
